        "default": "MATCH_STATUS_UNSPECIFIED",
        "title": "- SUCCESS: 匹配成功\n - PRICE_VARIANCE: 价格差异\n - QUANTITY_VARIANCE: 数量差异\n - MISSING_GOODS_RECEIPT: 缺少收货记录"
      },
      "invoiceMatchVariance": {
